<DOC><DOCNO> ZF32-001-356 </DOCNO><DOCID>11 624 910</DOCID><JOURNAL>Newsbytes  Dec 13 1991* Full Text COPYRIGHT Newsbytes Inc. 1991.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>Shiva bundles network software with Fastpath 5.andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Wallach, Naor.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Shiva Corp. (Marketing)StarNine Technologies Inc. (Products)Neon Software Inc. (Marketing).andO;Product:   Shiva FastPath (Gateway device) (Marketing)Mail*Link SMTP (Electronic mail system) (Marketing)RouterChecker (Network management software) (Marketing).andO;Topic:     Promotion of ProductMarketing StrategyConnectivityGateways (Connector)Electronic mail systemsNetwork management software.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>Shiva Bundles Network Software With Fastpath 5 12/13/91 CAMBRIDGE,MASSACHUSETTS, U.S.A., 1991 DEC 13 (NB) -- Shiva Corporation wants to make iteven more attractive for you to buy their internetworking products.andP;  Shiva isbundling two software products and a bunch of coupons with their Fastpath 5Ethernet to Appletalk gateway.andM;Participating in the promotion are StarNine and Neon.andP;  StarNine is the makerof Mail Link SMTP (Simple Mail Transfer Protocol), an electronic mailtransfer application that allows Macintoshes using their native e-mail tools(like InBox, Microsoft Mail, or QuickMail) to have access to the world ofUnix mail systems through the use of SMTP.andP;  Among other services, SMTP allowsaccess to the Internet which is a very large and comprehensive mail system inoperation throughout the country and the world.andM;StarNine will give you a two-user license when you purchase Shiva's Fastpath.andO;This is essentially a teaser package since it isn't likely that two Macintoshusers are all that will require this service on the network.andP;  Once you dodecide that you would like to buy more licenses, StarNine includes a couponin the package for significant discounts on more licenses.andM;Neon Software is also participating by incorporating a copy of itsRouterChecker software in this promotion.andP;  RouterChecker allows the networkadministrators track and monitor all routers on the network from a Macintoshthat is also somewhere on that network.andP;  RouterChecker also maintainslistings of router types, locations, and network addresses.andM;Fastpath 5 is Shiva's latest version of its popular router product.andP;  Itallows routing between Appletalk Phase I and II networks to communicate withEthernet networks.andP;  Fastpath 5 supports TCP/IP, DECnet, and IPTalk on theEthernet side.andP;  Included in the package is a copy of Shiva's Net Managersoftware which allows users to configure and manage their Shiva products fromany single location on the network.andM;(Naor Wallach/19911206/Press Contact: Carol McGarry, Shiva Corp.,andO;617-876-1188)</TEXT></DOC>